strapiEvent.name: Birds & Beverages
strapiEvent.location: Botanical Garden of the Ozarks - Fayetteville, AR
strapiEvent.description:
Socialize, learn something new, and have fun at this special event with North Song Wild Bird Rehabilitation and Wild Birds Unlimited for a very special event!

Registration includes 3 drink tickets of your choice. Alcoholic and nonalcoholic drinks available.

$35/members or $45/nonmembers
